727618f-a.text:
Northern Boulevard, north side, east from Parsons Boulevard to 146th Street. The first house, now abandoned, is the J. Bramwell house of 1891. The site is being offered for sale.
The other homes are of modern design.
P. L. Sperr  April 13, 1927
